          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h4>Mobile Integration</h4><p>In 2018 Aetrex acquired SOLS, the leading developer of mobile device foot-scanning applications, and launched the Albert Control Panel CRM, which provides partners access to all data points collected at the scanners. The control panel stores a wide range of data about consumers’ feet which can be used for R&D, merchandising, and to create powerful, personalized digital marketing campaigns to targeted consumers.</p>",
